0cd71653-9296-4004-8f72-ded3723e00a1.title: Mage of Zamorak
0cd71653-9296-4004-8f72-ded3723e00a1.text:
Ah, you again.
What was it you wanted?
The Wilderness is hardly the appropriate place for a
conversation now, is it?

options.text: I'd like to buy some runes!
遰 Where do you get your runes from?
All hail Zamorak!
Nothing, thanks.

e8f2d608-a2d5-4a89-9681-54cb32bad3ef.title: <player>
e8f2d608-a2d5-4a89-9681-54cb32bad3ef.text: I'd like to buy some runes!

5459ce56-d9e7-4c03-a2fb-e233ca626b22.title: Mage of Zamorak
5459ce56-d9e7-4c03-a2fb-e233ca626b22.text:
I do not conduct business in this pathetic city.
Speak to me in the wilderness if you desire to purchase
runes from me.

7025fa04-e951-49fb-aa3e-26c5350fb845.title: <player>
7025fa04-e951-49fb-aa3e-26c5350fb845.text: Pretty please with sugar and cherries on top?

eb7357c9-2fbc-4d8b-8cfb-529bd4a27f76.title: Mage of Zamorak
eb7357c9-2fbc-4d8b-8cfb-529bd4a27f76.text: Stranger, I warn you I have a low tolerance for idiocy.

21d08675-3348-47c6-aa73-caac059dfd69.title: Mage of Zamorak
21d08675-3348-47c6-aa73-caac059dfd69.text:
Now are you going to stand here all day annoying me,
or was there something that you actually wanted?

options.text: I'm going to stand here annoying you.
Where do you get your runes from?
All hail Zamorak!
Nothing, thanks.

a0d36a59-08c9-4248-aa92-36fb76796723.title: <player>
a0d36a59-08c9-4248-aa92-36fb76796723.text:
Actually, that standing here annoying you thing sounds
pretty good.

fe9b4eaa-c912-4287-b632-b6c16d697388.title: <player>
fe9b4eaa-c912-4287-b632-b6c16d697388.text:
All hail Zamorak!
He's the man!
If he can't do it, maybe some other guy can!

4e52335d-9096-4708-a8c1-95fc13962072.title: Mage of Zamorak
4e52335d-9096-4708-a8c1-95fc13962072.text:
...Okay.
I appreciate your enthusiasm for Lord Zamorak
stranger, but what exactly was it that you wanted?

options.text: I'd like to buy some runes!
Where do you get your runes from?
Nothing, thanks.

5cbc9ca7-f2de-4d39-a564-ed4dbf81936a.title: <player>
5cbc9ca7-f2de-4d39-a564-ed4dbf81936a.text:
I didn't really want anything, thanks.
I just like talking to random people I meet around the
world.

6acea933-fa23-4ed8-bab3-2fe900a57db9.title: Mage of Zamorak
6acea933-fa23-4ed8-bab3-2fe900a57db9.text:
...I see.
Well, in the future, do not waste my time, or you will
feel the wrath of Zamorak upon you.

b01621ab-cb45-4977-9d86-4d3288a93d45.title: <player>
b01621ab-cb45-4977-9d86-4d3288a93d45.text:
Where do you get your runes from?
No offence, but people around here don't exactly like
'your type'.

6d8708eb-fa7d-45ae-b046-8262caef5b0c.title: <player>
6d8708eb-fa7d-45ae-b046-8262caef5b0c.text:
You know...
Scary bearded men in dark clothing with unhealthy
obsessions with destruction and stuff.

1d923d58-0e36-44d8-a0d2-9e1f45e0f525.title: Mage of Zamorak
1d923d58-0e36-44d8-a0d2-9e1f45e0f525.text:
Hmmm.
Well, you may be right, the foolish Saradominists that
own this pathetic city don't appreciate loyal Zamorakians,
it is true.

a3f2790e-ea2d-42c3-8f64-ca0d3b1a7400.title: <player>
a3f2790e-ea2d-42c3-8f64-ca0d3b1a7400.text:
So you can't be getting your runes anywhere around
here...

d0f8cf69-cacf-4fc3-9580-004f37f818ab.title: Mage of Zamorak
d0f8cf69-cacf-4fc3-9580-004f37f818ab.text:
That is correct stranger.
The mysteries of manufacturing Runes is a closely
guarded secret of the Zamorakian brotherhood.

977a04a5-43cf-4084-a4d7-2633a280eea0.title: <player>
977a04a5-43cf-4084-a4d7-2633a280eea0.text:
Well, someday I will discover those &9Rune Mysteries&r for
myself!
You watch and see!

6ebf02c0-3d83-4d2a-8d40-21f1ce2be27e.title: Mage of Zamorak
6ebf02c0-3d83-4d2a-8d40-21f1ce2be27e.text:
Ha Ha Ha!
I think not stranger!

83364762-736c-489f-9ee0-525c196802f7.title: <player>
83364762-736c-489f-9ee0-525c196802f7.text:
Oh, you mean the whole teleporting to the Rune
Essence mine, mining some essence, then using the
talismans to locate the Rune Temples, then binding
runes there?

bc3a7823-1082-4975-bfa6-bdca6d28721c.title: Mage of Zamorak
bc3a7823-1082-4975-bfa6-bdca6d28721c.text:
Tell me, this is important:
You know of the ancient temples?
You have been to a place where this 'rune essence'
material is freely available?

073852ba-fac9-499b-b876-e26f4665a0f8.title: Mage of Zamorak
073852ba-fac9-499b-b876-e26f4665a0f8.text: How did you get to such a place?

28e1338a-dffd-42d0-9b2f-32443c112b5e.title: <player>
28e1338a-dffd-42d0-9b2f-32443c112b5e.text:
Well, I helped deliver some research notes to Sedridor
at the Wizards Tower, and he teleported me to a huge
mine he said was hidden off to the North somewhere
where I could mine essence.

c62abc02-dcaf-4ca3-8f91-29434b7e5975.title: Mage of Zamorak
c62abc02-dcaf-4ca3-8f91-29434b7e5975.text:
And there is an abundant supply of this 'essence' there
you say?

aa7c2b17-eed9-4a14-9c0e-35fd5f944072.title: <player>
aa7c2b17-eed9-4a14-9c0e-35fd5f944072.text:
Yes, but I thought you said that you knew how to make
runes?
All this stuff is fairly basic knowledge I thought.

f6974a1e-8694-4354-8ba9-47bdcaa8449f.title: Mage of Zamorak
f6974a1e-8694-4354-8ba9-47bdcaa8449f.text:
We occasionally manage to plunder small samples of this
'essence' and we have recently discovered these temples
you speak of, but I have never heard of these talismans
before, and I was certainly not aware that this 'essence'

4e262f32-c50b-4f90-a926-9279110cb5a0.title: Mage of Zamorak
4e262f32-c50b-4f90-a926-9279110cb5a0.text:
substance is a heavily stockpiled resource at the Wizards
Tower.

b9d4d9e7-be89-4926-8b36-dd0481e548d0.title: Mage of Zamorak
b9d4d9e7-be89-4926-8b36-dd0481e548d0.text:
For many years there has been a struggle for power
on this world.
You may dispute the morality of each side as you wish,
but the stalemate that exists between my Lord Zamorak

aa9d5f88-381f-4cb5-87f4-3ec17ed173b1.title: Mage of Zamorak
aa9d5f88-381f-4cb5-87f4-3ec17ed173b1.text:
and that pathetic meddling fool Saradomin has meant
that our struggles have become more secretive.
We exist in a 'cold war' if you will, each side fearful of
letting the other gain too much power, and each side

29b696fa-f103-4e55-94d3-86eb2c65bd4f.title: Mage of Zamorak
29b696fa-f103-4e55-94d3-86eb2c65bd4f.text:
equally fearful of entering into open warfare for fear of
bringing our struggles to the attention of... other
beings.

5e0d34b3-c4c5-488b-bc52-e59359a70b0e.title: Mage of Zamorak
5e0d34b3-c4c5-488b-bc52-e59359a70b0e.text:
Indeed.
Amongst others.
But you now tell me that the Saradominist Wizards
have the capability to mass produce runes, I can only

b1ac295c-6aab-4209-b89a-ace84ed8fc8d.title: Mage of Zamorak
b1ac295c-6aab-4209-b89a-ace84ed8fc8d.text:
conclude that they have been doing so secretly for some
time now.

0b473554-0d6d-4ae5-a8e0-0883824a458a.title: Mage of Zamorak
0b473554-0d6d-4ae5-a8e0-0883824a458a.text:
I implore you adventurer, you may or may not agree
with my aims, but you cannot allow such a one-sided
shift in the balance of power to occur.

3426cc05-05c9-4372-8cd3-a3440bc037ae.title: Mage of Zamorak
3426cc05-05c9-4372-8cd3-a3440bc037ae.text:
Will you help me and my fellow Zamorakians to access
this 'essence' mine?
In return I will share with you the research we have
gathered.

options.text: 遰 Yes.
No.

04b7fe06-3ddc-4d6e-a8ed-1c1c5ef1b06f.title: <player>
04b7fe06-3ddc-4d6e-a8ed-1c1c5ef1b06f.text:
No, I don't want anything to do with you and trying
to bribe me into helping isn't going to work on me.

1394753d-bea4-4d23-b312-a46fe7770f3e.title: Mage of Zamorak
1394753d-bea4-4d23-b312-a46fe7770f3e.text:
As you wish, stranger.
I will achieve my goals elsewhere.

e1a424cd-ed0f-43bf-a89d-14a801489680.title: <player>
e1a424cd-ed0f-43bf-a89d-14a801489680.text:
Okay, I'll help you.
What can I do?

85551f64-947b-486d-998a-2d9ca095f720.title: Mage of Zamorak
85551f64-947b-486d-998a-2d9ca095f720.text:
All I need from you is the spell that will teleport me to
this essence mine.
That should be sufficient for the armies of Zamorak to
once more begin stockpiling magic for war.

1faeac7c-cdc6-4806-b5c0-f70b325e4079.title: <player>
1faeac7c-cdc6-4806-b5c0-f70b325e4079.text:
Oh.
Erm....
I don't actually know that spell.

76735684-d7c4-44c9-af90-455455a2064b.title: Mage of Zamorak
76735684-d7c4-44c9-af90-455455a2064b.text:
What?
Then how do you access this location?

e6047aa1-c4ea-4376-acc3-94edff337e76.title: <player>
e6047aa1-c4ea-4376-acc3-94edff337e76.text:
Oh, well, people who do know the spell teleport me there
directly.
Apparently they wouldn't teach it to me to try and keep
the location secret.

2a221a8e-65b9-4084-a027-ed0f7314143c.title: Mage of Zamorak
2a221a8e-65b9-4084-a027-ed0f7314143c.text:
Hmmm.
Yes, yes I see.
Very well then, you may still assist us in finding this
mysterious essence mine.

5257b3c9-0147-42ab-91a1-606c42436685.title: Mage of Zamorak
5257b3c9-0147-42ab-91a1-606c42436685.text:
I'll give you a scrying orb.
I have cast a standard cypher spell upon it, so that it
will absorb mystical energies that it is exposed to.

08481ab1-f978-4432-b20e-22ac0fed4244.title: Mage of Zamorak
08481ab1-f978-4432-b20e-22ac0fed4244.text:
Bring it with you and teleport to the rune essence
location, and it will absorb the mechanics of the spell and
allow us to reverse-engineer the magic behind it.

30469e51-e1d6-4c69-9a84-8970ac227e49.title: Mage of Zamorak
30469e51-e1d6-4c69-9a84-8970ac227e49.text:
The important part is that you must teleport to the
essence location from three entirely separate locations.

c80cebec-e78a-4c7a-880f-54452a4d87ee.title: Mage of Zamorak
c80cebec-e78a-4c7a-880f-54452a4d87ee.text:
More than three may be helpful to us, but we need a
minimum of three in order to triangulate the position of
this essence mine.

5b876702-a439-4839-ad4c-1cad6c9eb39d.title: Mage of Zamorak
5b876702-a439-4839-ad4c-1cad6c9eb39d.text:
Here's the scrying orb.
If you encounter any difficulties speak to me again.

c9e9fdd3-4966-44b6-aa8a-9275ac23d980.title: Mage of Zamorak
c9e9fdd3-4966-44b6-aa8a-9275ac23d980.text:
Well?
Have you managed to use my scrying orb to obtain the
information yet?

cf96bdd4-1d5d-49e6-80cf-b3e06414019d.title: <player>
cf96bdd4-1d5d-49e6-80cf-b3e06414019d.text:
No...
Actually, I had something I wanted to ask you...

83beba52-4178-42ae-ae05-03f397a5da89.title: Mage of Zamorak
83beba52-4178-42ae-ae05-03f397a5da89.text:
I assumed the task to be self-explanatory.
What is it you wish to know?

options.text: What am I supposed to be doing again?
What's in this for me, anyway?
You're not going to use this for evil are you?
Can I have another crystal ball thing?

21c42df5-3a61-4c73-aba8-d744738e2d06.title: <player>
21c42df5-3a61-4c73-aba8-d744738e2d06.text:
If I help you with this...
I'd just like to keep my conscience clear and know that
you're not going to use whatever information I give to
you in the pursuit of evil and badness and stuff.

97ae9d0f-e4ad-4b9c-83be-95a239805cac.title: Mage of Zamorak
97ae9d0f-e4ad-4b9c-83be-95a239805cac.text:
Very well, if it makes you feel any better;
I promise you that any knowledge you provide me with,
absolutely will not be used in the service of anything
more evil than what I was already planning on doing

abe6eeeb-8c7b-4ca9-8c66-c650a73989b2.title: Mage of Zamorak
abe6eeeb-8c7b-4ca9-8c66-c650a73989b2.text: I hope that sets your conscience at rest.

22e92e7a-188a-47a3-8372-162b1ffb0afd.title: <player>
22e92e7a-188a-47a3-8372-162b1ffb0afd.text:
You know...
In a weird way it actually does...

options.text: What am I supposed to be doing again?
What's in this for me, anyway?
Can I have another crystal ball thing?
Nope, that's it!

1be3cfc1-2b70-4909-8fbe-0cee734e67c1.title: <player>
1be3cfc1-2b70-4909-8fbe-0cee734e67c1.text: No, I think I have everything clear in my head now.

38422c85-58ad-4ff1-9691-9c3f0705679b.title: Mage of Zamorak
38422c85-58ad-4ff1-9691-9c3f0705679b.text:
That is good to hear, stranger.
Bring me my orb back when you have successfully
made those teleports.

ac6f6c7d-a765-443c-a1d0-eb487192fd65.title: <player>
ac6f6c7d-a765-443c-a1d0-eb487192fd65.text:
I just want to know one thing:
What's in this for me?

d504b18d-3086-40f2-8f2a-51cea1ac3eb0.title: Mage of Zamorak
d504b18d-3086-40f2-8f2a-51cea1ac3eb0.text:
Well now, I can certainly understand that attitude.
Let me assure you of this; from what you tell me, you
have discovered a way of gaining these 'essence stones'
quickly and efficiently, yet it sounds as though your

7e99fa3a-47db-465f-b9eb-01a50f49997e.title: Mage of Zamorak
7e99fa3a-47db-465f-b9eb-01a50f49997e.text:
method of reaching the temples which are used to bind
these essences is random and counter-productive.

49fb0881-aec3-49a6-b07c-5b24775a6497.title: Mage of Zamorak
49fb0881-aec3-49a6-b07c-5b24775a6497.text:
I, on the other hand, have information on quickly
accessing these temples, yet my methods of procuring
this 'essence' are time consuming and useless as a
means of mass production.

632b403a-f818-49e0-a261-c497f36aca1f.title: Mage of Zamorak
632b403a-f818-49e0-a261-c497f36aca1f.text:
I think you can see for yourself how this may benefit
both of us;
You allow me the knowledge of finding plentiful essence,
and I will in return show you the secret of these

options.text: What am I supposed to be doing again?
You're not going to use this for evil are you?
Can I have another crystal ball thing?
Nope, that's it!

ab0d46ce-d110-4753-b1b6-d2edfe988253.title: <player>
ab0d46ce-d110-4753-b1b6-d2edfe988253.text:
Please excuse me, I have a very bad short term
memory.
What exactly am I supposed to be doing again?

8dab6fed-4cd7-4ae1-a3ee-6097724105bb.title: Mage of Zamorak
8dab6fed-4cd7-4ae1-a3ee-6097724105bb.text:
I am slightly concerned about your capability for this
mission, if you cannot even recall such a simple task...

f1d5bdad-ea9a-48b7-a66f-227e26d2cafe.title: Mage of Zamorak
f1d5bdad-ea9a-48b7-a66f-227e26d2cafe.text:
All I wish for you to do is to teleport to this 'rune
essence' location from three different locations while
carrying the scrying orb I gave you.
It will collect the data as you teleport, and if you then

d36e597c-768c-4f9c-8b21-2ef4baeec90b.title: Mage of Zamorak
d36e597c-768c-4f9c-8b21-2ef4baeec90b.text:
bring it to me I will be able to use it to further my
own investigations.

b4c2eb09-3be4-4a3c-bcb0-f9a28692e77b.title: <player>
b4c2eb09-3be4-4a3c-bcb0-f9a28692e77b.text:
So you want me to teleport to the rune essence mine
while carrying the scrying ball?

a4870161-4180-4df5-bce5-f8a6138fa080.title: <player>
a4870161-4180-4df5-bce5-f8a6138fa080.text:
And I need to teleport into the essence mine from
three different locations?

7c010224-bf48-4da8-984f-7dbb5bf564a4.title: <player>
7c010224-bf48-4da8-984f-7dbb5bf564a4.text:
Okay...
I think I understand that...

41a5caa8-8387-488b-a28a-74d6c9c3cf9e.title: Mage of Zamorak
41a5caa8-8387-488b-a28a-74d6c9c3cf9e.text:
That is good to know.
Is there something else you need clarifying?

options.text: What's in this for me, anyway?
You're not going to use this for evil are you?
Can I have another crystal ball thing?
Nope, that's it!

3667f3fa-53c8-4712-a5fb-24d6cdd011ae.title: <player>
3667f3fa-53c8-4712-a5fb-24d6cdd011ae.text:
This crystal ball thingy is kind of nifty.
Can I have another one?

6f299515-29cd-44a0-981b-4dd3bd2416b5.title: Mage of Zamorak
6f299515-29cd-44a0-981b-4dd3bd2416b5.text:
It is not a 'crystal ball thingy'.
It is a precision made magical instrument called a
scrying orb.
Do you have some particular need for another one?

224e7444-64bb-4cd3-82e8-3653cabc38a6.title: <player>
224e7444-64bb-4cd3-82e8-3653cabc38a6.text:
Not really, I just like to fill up my bank with cool
looking stuff.

246e9621-2891-4b6d-ba11-bb36935f55d5.title: Mage of Zamorak
246e9621-2891-4b6d-ba11-bb36935f55d5.text:
Then no, no you may not have another one.
One will be sufficient for the task at hand.

eccf0d17-5aa0-483f-9001-90c562dc1e8a.title: <player>
eccf0d17-5aa0-483f-9001-90c562dc1e8a.text:
Erm...
But I lost the one you gave me...
Can I have another one then?

743e6206-5cbc-4838-93a4-e952c01472f5.title: Mage of Zamorak
743e6206-5cbc-4838-93a4-e952c01472f5.text:
No you haven't.
I can see that you have it there in your backpack.
Now quit your foolishness and get on with the task in
hand!

87ad0d0e-ed52-4a62-bb8e-0979e7214897.title: Mage of Zamorak
87ad0d0e-ed52-4a62-bb8e-0979e7214897.text:
What happened to the last one?!
Fine but do not lose this one.

6f1d3800-2afe-4ee6-8956-7fa9e1b845bf.title: Mage of Zamorak
6f1d3800-2afe-4ee6-8956-7fa9e1b845bf.text:
Well?
Have you managed to use my scrying orb to obtain the
information yet?

59397a04-2494-4524-9981-afcc802af10d.title: <player>
59397a04-2494-4524-9981-afcc802af10d.text:
Yes I have!
I've got it right here!

cc4e9eb4-c1a5-456c-9e7f-eb93e73afc99.title: Mage of Zamorak
cc4e9eb4-c1a5-456c-9e7f-eb93e73afc99.text:
Excellent.
Give it here, and I shall examine the findings.
Speak to me in a small while.

91ab2e17-e7d7-4b54-a73f-122adfc205f3.title: <player>
91ab2e17-e7d7-4b54-a73f-122adfc205f3.text:
So... that's my end of the deal upheld.
What do I get in return?

02cdeaf9-a7fd-41f6-b9ee-e9e0eb744801.title: Mage of Zamorak
02cdeaf9-a7fd-41f6-b9ee-e9e0eb744801.text: Indeed, a deal is always a deal.

ea7b7747-4b42-46ed-a916-1309fbb8054f.title: Mage of Zamorak
ea7b7747-4b42-46ed-a916-1309fbb8054f.text:
I offer you three things as reward for your efforts on
behalf of my Lord Zamorak;

33518959-f4ce-44f9-8ab5-c90475b60138.title: Mage of Zamorak
33518959-f4ce-44f9-8ab5-c90475b60138.text:
The first is knowledge.
I offer you my collected research on the abyss.
I also offer you 1000 points of experience in
Runecrafting for your trouble.

3cfea31d-641b-4541-ac0f-bf02e347f372.title: Mage of Zamorak
3cfea31d-641b-4541-ac0f-bf02e347f372.text:
Your second gift is convenience.
Here, you may take this pouch I discovered amidst my
research.
You will find it to have certain... interesting properties.

dc75379f-3c91-4196-ae51-53155a790928.title: Mage of Zamorak
dc75379f-3c91-4196-ae51-53155a790928.text:
Your final gift is that of movement.
I will from now on offer you a teleport to the abyss
whenever you should require it.

2a858af4-17a2-476f-b48c-8ec453b83298.title: <player>
2a858af4-17a2-476f-b48c-8ec453b83298.text:
Huh?
Abyss?
What are you talking about?
You told me that you would help me with Runecrafting!

2fd07277-bde0-4ca7-a44e-e882c9869686.title: Mage of Zamorak
2fd07277-bde0-4ca7-a44e-e882c9869686.text:
And so I have done.
Read my research notes, they may enlighten you
somewhat.

options.text: So what is this 'abyss' stuff?
Is this abyss dangerous?
Can you teleport me there now?

4e19caac-4d14-4324-9e5a-ec5e6384df59.title: <player>
4e19caac-4d14-4324-9e5a-ec5e6384df59.text:
Well, I reckon I'm prepared to go there now.
Beam me there, or whatever it is that you do!

2053627b-d6be-4775-8c86-5b6d075604fc.title: Mage of Zamorak
2053627b-d6be-4775-8c86-5b6d075604fc.text:
No, not from here.
The use of my Lord Zamoraks magic in this land will
draw too much attention to myself.

244f55df-edce-4b09-82f2-6e14302640f6.title: Mage of Zamorak
244f55df-edce-4b09-82f2-6e14302640f6.text:
Meet me in the wilderness where you spoke to me
before, and right click to find the 'teleport' option.

0db3ca69-a54f-4d0c-850d-6842fddfb139.title: Mage of Zamorak
0db3ca69-a54f-4d0c-850d-6842fddfb139.text:
I trust you do not wish to have too lengthy a
conversation in such a dangerous place.

19fe5e6f-1381-42c0-bf92-2416da9ea721.title: Mage of Zamorak
19fe5e6f-1381-42c0-bf92-2416da9ea721.text:
I should be able to improve my stock of runes thanks to
your assistance locating the essence site too, so feel free
to stop by if you require any specific runes.

739d8f12-38bb-41a6-be68-ddfeeca3431b.title: <player>
739d8f12-38bb-41a6-be68-ddfeeca3431b.text:
So...
This 'abyss' place...
Is it dangerous?

6c8cb540-b9fb-420b-b196-62284ec396f6.title: Mage of Zamorak
6c8cb540-b9fb-420b-b196-62284ec396f6.text: Well, the creatures there ARE particularly offensive...

e5328c92-2d85-40bd-8a22-f04263e63d88.title: Mage of Zamorak
e5328c92-2d85-40bd-8a22-f04263e63d88.text:
No, I mean they hunt and attack any visitors to their
dimension on sight.
This is not the danger however.

4c1b2eac-f228-438d-93fa-7a802d2d7a54.title: Mage of Zamorak
4c1b2eac-f228-438d-93fa-7a802d2d7a54.text:
No.
Unfortunately the magic we have had to use to retain a
portal to the abyss open and effective is derived from
Lord Zamorak himself.

a4d3d2e8-760e-4489-8c09-88c6f9b204c0.title: <player>
a4d3d2e8-760e-4489-8c09-88c6f9b204c0.text: And that's a bad thing somehow...?

6b245dc4-3921-4a2c-98bd-61c69a782892.title: Mage of Zamorak
6b245dc4-3921-4a2c-98bd-61c69a782892.text:
Well, he has his occasional quirks.
In this case it means that when you enter this
dimension you will be 'skulled' and your prayer will be
drained.

5b4eb66b-5f08-4e1a-9757-81881b4e1563.title: Mage of Zamorak
5b4eb66b-5f08-4e1a-9757-81881b4e1563.text:
This makes it somewhat more dangerous than other
places you may be used to.

d5025c40-d79d-4be7-9510-e59c5e7bb11f.title: Mage of Zamorak
d5025c40-d79d-4be7-9510-e59c5e7bb11f.text: Was there anything else you wanted?

d80bcd69-38de-47b0-a155-553367a75e20.title: <player>
d80bcd69-38de-47b0-a155-553367a75e20.text:
Uh...
I really don't see how this talk about an 'abyss' relates
to Runecrafting in the slightest...

2733259c-49ee-42ff-b779-42895a8a9785.title: Mage of Zamorak
2733259c-49ee-42ff-b779-42895a8a9785.text:
My primary research responsibility was not towards the
manufacture of runes, this is true.

b8c8c92d-5ac7-4c7d-9a53-1e812c0c5861.title: Mage of Zamorak
b8c8c92d-5ac7-4c7d-9a53-1e812c0c5861.text:
Rather, I was investigating an error that occurred to
one of our initiates in a routine teleportation
experiment.

44978fda-d71f-4a8a-a250-7be744027000.title: Mage of Zamorak
44978fda-d71f-4a8a-a250-7be744027000.text:
My discovery was this 'abyssal' space, and as a side
effect, as documented in the research notes I have
given you, I discovered the existence of these 'temples'
used to create runes.

51d3c38f-a423-4688-a976-4792a905d23c.title: Mage of Zamorak
51d3c38f-a423-4688-a976-4792a905d23c.text:
Fortunate for both of us, I would say.
As I say, read my research notes, it should all become
clear.

2d12eafb-aa38-4967-86a4-0fa2b393229f.title: Mage of Zamorak
2d12eafb-aa38-4967-86a4-0fa2b393229f.text:
My colleague inside the abyss may be of help to you as
well.
